title: Set realistic goals
desc: Setting achievable fitness goals is essential for keeping yourself motivated. Start by defining your long-term goals and then break them down into smaller, achievable milestones. For example, if you want to lose weight, aim to lose a specific amount of weight per week or month. Remember, the key is to be realistic and set goals that are challenging yet attainable.
